messages.text: nothing much! are you going to the cast party tonight?
yes, i’m planning to arrive around 10
by the way, are you nervous for our final performance tonight?
i’m trying not to think too hard about it
i can’t believe we’re almost done with this show!
shakespeare is my favorite but those lines are a mouthful for sure
yeah, strange that we won’t be acting together anymore
i know, it’s been a lot of fun
it’s been awesome getting to know everyone in general
we didn’t even have an arts program at my old school
yeah, you transferred here mid-year right?
i’ve been meaning to ask but didn’t want to be rude
i have always wanted to go
ok so since it’s your first show with us, you obviously don’t know
are you going to throw tomatoes at me or something
before the closing night of every show
the cast meets early and plays truth or dare together
i don’t know if i’m ready for that
well at least now you have some time to think about it!
because i’m not ready to share my dirty secrets with the whole cast
if she’s in the cast then i know her…
ok so you might know her
but she’s very different than you
blows the rest of the cast out of the water honestly
i’m the lead in the show
don’t go getting a big head now
she’s really friendly, always lights up a room
i would just like to point out that i texted you first
if that’s not friendly i don’t know what is
well you should tell her how you feel!!
truth or dare might be the perfect time!
confessing my feelings in front of all my new acquaintances
anyway i don’t want to risk making things awkward before closing night
her and i still have to do a show together
and we will see each other at the cast party
well i’m sure whoever she is
she will definitely feel the same
you’re kind of a hot commodity
how many nice, good-looking british guys do you see running around in sacramento lol
anyway, it would definitely make things awkward if i told this girl
because i’m going home to bath for the summer
i won’t be back until senior year starts in the fall
yeah that’ll suck for her lol
how do you think she might take it?
i guess it really just depends on the girl
well, for example, how would you take it
i would probably say you would be worth it. you’re a good guy
alright i think i’m going to tell her
now to just do the deed
i feel the same way about you, danny
i’m going to miss you but i think we get along really well and i’m glad you feel the same way
you’ve basically been trying to tell me how to feel for this entire conversation
i feel like you may have gotten the wrong idea somewhere
i was talking about sandra actually
and we still have to act together tonight
can we just “act” like that never happened? ha ha ha…
that was hilarious i couldn’t keep that up for long lol
of course i was talking about you silly
but i’m glad i’m not completely delusional
you’re definitely the most talented one in the cast
well after all, this is sacramento, not broadway
so are you ready to break a leg tonight?
guess you’re all set for truth or dare too
since you already spilled the beans and all
i am a man of many mysteries
who knows how many secrets i have yet to spill
now who has the big head
i promise you i have no idea what you’re talking about
see you at 6, don’t be late!
